\sum\limits_{i=1}^\infty n^2 \dot (x)^{n-1} 
x=\frac{5}{6}
\sum\limits_{i=1}^\infty n^2 \dot (x)^{n-1}= -\frac {x+1} {(x-1)^3}
|x| < 1
\sum_{n\geq 1} n x^{n-1}
\sum_{n \geq 2} n (n-1) x^{n-2}
(1-x)^{-1} = \sum_{n=0}^{\infty} x^n
 \sum_{n = 1}^{\infty} n^2 x^{n-1}  = x \sum_{n=2}^{\infty} n(n-1) x^{n-2} + \sum_{n = 1}^{\infty} n x^{n-1} 
